Metavariable P:Statement
Metavariable Q:Statement
Metavariable R:Statement

Rule (DisjunctionLeftIntroduction,RightAddtion)
  Premise
    P
  Conclusion
    P ∨ Q

Rule (DisjunctionRightIntroduction,LeftAddition)
  Premise
    Q
  Conclusion
    P ∨ Q

Rule (DisjunctionElimination,ProofByCases)
  Premises
    P ⇒ R
    Q ⇒ R
    P ∨ Q
  Conclusion
    R
